{"tid":1237884,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一信致監警會","createTime":"2019-06-17T15:55:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-18T03:32:39.000Z","uid":263756,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"a1228f83509df2bd572a0ba3c4806e8fea000ee7","tid":1237884,"uid":263756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T15:55:48.000Z","msg":"既然盧偉聰話有咩不滿可向監警會 / 警察投訴科投訴，我地就要向監警會投訴，要求徹查警方於6.12過份使用武力。<br />\n<br />\n如果大家有個別警察過份使用武力的證據或資料，就一定要向監警會投訴！<br />\n<br />\n即使最終可能不了了之，但不能放棄任何一個機會去追究警方於6.12的所作所為。<br />\n<br />\n監警會投訴警察課處理投訴的程序：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mRTOgTV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmRTOgTV.png&h=8fd3b8e6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n監警會網址：<a href=\"https://www.ipcc.gov.hk/tc/complaints/contact_CAPO.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ipcc.gov.hk%2Ftc%2Fcomplaints%2Fcontact_CAPO.html&d=bJSHN4a6RFajNgW6euKvYUuhYyo0AmqkWOXXUYRqYBI%3D&h=10abfcb5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ipcc.gov.hk/tc/complaints/contact_CAPO.html</a><br />\n警察投訴科網址：<a href=\"https://www2.erc.police.gov.hk/cmiserc/EGIS-HK-Web_NEW_UI/ereport_details?report=CMPLNT_AGNST_POLICE_OFCR&amp;fontSize=100\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.erc.police.gov.hk%2Fcmiserc%2FEGIS-HK-Web_NEW_UI%2Fereport_details%3Freport%3DCMPLNT_AGNST_POLICE_OFCR%26fontSize%3D100&d=bJSHN4a6RFajNgW6euKvYUuhYyo0AmqkWOXXUYRqYBI%3D&h=807ab3a4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www2.erc.police.gov.hk/cmiserc/EGIS-HK-Web_NEW_UI/ereport_details?report=CMPLNT_AGNST_POLICE_OFCR&amp;fontSize=100</a>"},{"pid":"e1736472a5613bc6c8027ce96e964bcf2cbbfbd5","tid":1237884,"uid":167177,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T16:03:57.000Z","msg":"去公務員事務局投訴更有效，至少唔係自己人查自己人！"},{"pid":"7f88065221af087d1d77a869ee08a582d5a03690","tid":1237884,"uid":208296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e1736472a5613bc6c8027ce96e964bcf2cbbfbd5","tid":1237884,"uid":167177,"